    "name": "拯救阿曼  SAVE AMANI",
    "steam_appid": 3153280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "《拯救阿曼 SAVE AMANI》是一款关于战争冒险游戏。玩家将帮助一个名叫阿曼的小男孩在战争中逃离各种危险。玩家可以感受到战争的残酷以及对人们生命和灵魂的破坏和伤害，从而唤起人们对和平的珍视和对战争中儿童的关注。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/c0a8482fa3ad724eba311e482b8c6c0b.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/c0a8482fa3ad724eba311e482b8c6c0b.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/c0a8482fa3ad724eba311e482b8c6c0b.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br><br>战争摧残下的城市，‌满目疮痍，‌一片狼藉。‌曾经辉煌的建筑如今化为断壁残垣，‌街道遍布碎石与焦土，‌硝烟弥漫，‌天空灰暗。‌战争的无情剥夺了城市的生机与活力，‌留下的是无尽的哀伤与沉痛的记忆。‌人们流离失所，‌家园破碎，‌战争的阴影笼罩着每一寸土地，‌令人心痛不已。‌<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/a8eefa5c83e162b3ee46555135553174.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/a8eefa5c83e162b3ee46555135553174.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/a8eefa5c83e162b3ee46555135553174.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>敌人潜伏于四面八方，‌持枪实弹的士兵随时可能现身，‌无人机在空中不间断地盘旋，‌机械狗在必经之路上巡逻，‌此外还需时刻警惕倒塌的墙体、‌隐藏于土壤中的地雷，‌以及可能从空中落下的炮弹，‌每一步都充满了未知与危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f88e7a9c4a9047a927c63722084b3254.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f88e7a9c4a9047a927c63722084b3254.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f88e7a9c4a9047a927c63722084b3254.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>务必注意躲藏，‌尽量远离敌方无人机，‌一旦被其扫描并锁定，阿曼将面临被射杀的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/428bdbdb890423600763613a59157316.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/428bdbdb890423600763613a59157316.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/428bdbdb890423600763613a59157316.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>可以操控自己的小型无人机，‌既能探索前方状况，‌又能有效地引开敌人，‌用途广泛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d433761c1df3959b2b771275192585b8.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d433761c1df3959b2b771275192585b8.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d433761c1df3959b2b771275192585b8.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>战争肆虐，‌孩童无辜，小男孩阿曼‌亲眼目睹家园破碎，‌亲人离散。‌昔日温暖怀抱，‌今成冰冷回忆，‌稚嫩心灵，‌承受无尽悲痛。<br>为缅怀逝去的老师，‌点燃蜡烛，‌献上最诚挚的祈愿与思念。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/9c10702042fbaa05639adead01c4b0c6.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/9c10702042fbaa05639adead01c4b0c6.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/9c10702042fbaa05639adead01c4b0c6.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>多个空间支持从第三人称视角切换至第一人称视角进行探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/6b941010549ab53506da997c57e9edf5.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/6b941010549ab53506da997c57e9edf5.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/6b941010549ab53506da997c57e9edf5.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>帮助阿曼寻找到那个二维码，‌只需戴上VR眼镜并扫描，‌便能让他沉浸在战争之前未被摧毁的虚幻场景之中，曾经的校园、‌课室、‌街道、‌图书馆、‌游乐场、中心广场~~~~，‌一切历历在目。‌每次戴上VR眼镜，‌阿曼的脸上都会绽放出笑容，‌因为他能再次见到昔日的亲人、同学、‌老师，‌以及那些曾经最熟悉的环境。‌<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/e633adcc93bcf9e8332c08e5b9f25309.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/e633adcc93bcf9e8332c08e5b9f25309.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/e633adcc93bcf9e8332c08e5b9f25309.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>然而，‌当摘下眼镜，‌现实再次映入眼帘，‌阿曼的心中便充满了无尽的悲伤。‌<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f25b2a5a54703f8f4c65983fec9a0f9f.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f25b2a5a54703f8f4c65983fec9a0f9f.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f25b2a5a54703f8f4c65983fec9a0f9f.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>曾经，‌小男孩阿曼如同冬日里的一缕阳光，‌笑容温暖而明媚，‌眼神中闪烁着纯真的光芒。‌他热爱阳光、‌温暖、‌云彩、‌大自然以及小动物。‌然而，‌如今他的眼神已不再闪烁，‌只能将自己藏匿于黑暗之中。‌似乎那些对每个人而言都触手可及的事物，‌对阿曼来说却成了遥不可及的奢望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d516e4fe34dbf945bf3f33df184fecb8.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d516e4fe34dbf945bf3f33df184fecb8.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/d516e4fe34dbf945bf3f33df184fecb8.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>一墙之隔，‌两个世界截然分开，‌翻越无望，‌但男孩阿曼仍需在危机四伏中，‌鼓起勇气，‌毅然前行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f6ded11cb2dcb3d91075187ac4b73ccd.poster.avif?t=1724047372\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f6ded11cb2dcb3d91075187ac4b73ccd.webm?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153280/extras/f6ded11cb2dcb3d91075187ac4b73ccd.mp4?t=1724047372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
